reviews.title: Too many ads
reviews.comment: Seems fun but there are way too many ads that interrupt you. Uninstalled before even finishing making mine.

reviews.title: I don\'t get it.
reviews.comment: I can see that this app is for creating something using game of thrones, but I am unclear as to what that is, and all you can do is share it on FB. Uninstalled.
reviews.author: Tony Clark

reviews.title: Too many ads
reviews.comment: Ads constantly pop up. Developer said they were removed and they are not. Uninstalled within 2 minutes (4 full page pop up ads later). No one wants that!!!
reviews.author: Wendilyn Printy
